#. js-lingui-id: sGuHDu
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "Nine Dots rebuilt Homeseller's operations on Twenty, with a custom data model shaped around their sales flow. Because Twenty is open and everything is accessible via API, they connected it to what the business actually needed: n8n for automated workflows (in-app workflows were not available at that time), Grafana for live dashboards fed from Twenty, and a custom AI layer to parse and extract structured insights from more than 2,000 WhatsApp messages a day."
